rame.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/8Mar_Zim-Vaccines_KM008-1920x1280.jpg 1920w, https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/8Mar_Zim-Vaccines_KM008-480x320.jpg 480w, https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/8Mar_Zim-Vaccines_KM008-270x180.jpg 270w, https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/8Mar_Zim-Vaccines_KM008-560x373.jpg 560w" sizes="(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px" /><img data-attachment-id="122193" data-permalink="https://www.newframe.com/slow-start-to-zimbabwes-vaccination-campaign/8mar_zim-vaccines_km005/" data-orig-file="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/8Mar_Zim-Vaccines_KM005-scaled.jpg" data-orig-size="2560,1707" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;1.4&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;ILCE-7M2&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;24 February 20201: A health worker shows off the  Sinopharm vaccine during the launch of the City of Bulawayo\u2019s vaccination programme. Bulawayo is Zimbabwe\u2019s second worst affected city with 5281 cases and 203 deaths recorded as at 2 March.&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1614161712&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;35&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.0025&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="8Mar_Zim-Vaccines_KM005" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/8Mar_Zim-Vaccines_KM005-960x640.jpg" data-large-file="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/8Mar_Zim-Vaccines_KM005-1440x960.jpg" loading="lazy" width="1440" height="960" src="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/8Mar_Zim-Vaccines_KM005-1440x960.jpg" alt="" data-id="122193" data-full-url="https://www.newframe.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/8Mar_Zim-Vaccines_KM005-scaled.jpg" data-link="https://www.newframe.com/?attachment_id=122193" cl